displayContent.description:
"Great spot for Thai and Cambodian food. I come here at least once a month and try many different dishes although my favorite is the curry. Prices are reasonable but they do get busy Friday and Saturday nights. A good place for take out too." - Lynn Byrd. "Good value for money. I like their lunch special which comes with soup. 

Green curry is good. Dishes with eggplant are excellent. 

Food can be spicy. I love spicy food as long as it adds flavor and not just heat. I found spice level 7/10 to be the sweet spot. " - Sai vignesh V.A

displayContent.description: "The food here is great! I haven't found many good Thai places in the south bay but the food here is really good and the service is great as well. I got the pineapple red curry and I would recommend it." - Zander Clucas. "Absolutely the best Thai food we have had for a long time. Fresh, excellent taste, great service and very reasonable price. Definitely coming back." - Patricia George
